headline: Federal Realty Appoints Joseph D. Fisher to Board of Trustees
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) today announced the appointment of Joseph D. Fisher to its Board of Trustees, effective January 1, 2026. Mr. Fisher will serve on the Board's Audit and Compensation and Human Capital Management Committees.

headline: How Investors Are Reacting To UDR (UDR) Earnings Guidance Upgrade and Share Buyback Announcement
summary: UDR, Inc. recently reported its third-quarter 2025 results, highlighting year-over-year growth in revenue and net income, and announced it completed a share buyback of 951,000 shares for US$34.98 million between July and October 2025. The company also raised its full-year 2025 earnings guidance, signaling management's confidence following stronger-than-expected quarterly performance and operational progress.
